text: ao mnoussa lok. chea karpit nasa anakneasar ban noam karpit pi mcheasa robsa puok anak mokkan puok anak . dau che neah chaur puok anakmean chomnue choh vea chea kar laobrapei samreab puok anak . te brasenbae puok anak brachheang vinh noh pitabrakd nasa avei del now leumekh cheachraen chean ning phendei kuchea kammosetthi robsa a l laoh . a l laoh mha doeng mha ktebandet
